// Part 1: Library Helpers
////////////////////////////

// 1.1: No-Ops

.

// 1.2: Memory Helpers
CLR . 1 0 SET RCLR 0 GET . 0 EQU . TST RCLR SHOULD CLEAR REGS END

// Part 2: Derived Functions
/////////////////////////////

// 2.1: Math Functions

CLR . 2 3 LT . 1 EQU . TST 2 < 3 SHOULD BE 1 END
CLR . 3 3 LT . 0 EQU . TST 3 < 3 SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 4 3 LT . 0 EQU . TST 4 < 3 SHOULD BE 0 END

CLR . 2 3 LTE . 1 EQU . TST 2 <= 3 SHOULD BE 1 END
CLR . 3 3 LTE . 1 EQU . TST 3 <= 3 SHOULD BE 1 END
CLR . 4 3 LTE . 0 EQU . TST 4 <= 3 SHOULD BE 0 END

CLR . 3 2 GT . 1 EQU . TST 3 > 2 SHOULD BE 1 END
CLR . 3 3 GT . 0 EQU . TST 3 > 3 SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 3 4 GT . 0 EQU . TST 3 > 4 SHOULD BE 0 END

// 2.2: Memory Functions

CLR . 1 DUP . EQU . TST DUP SHOULD DUP END

CLR . 1 2 DUP2 . ADD ADD ADD 6 EQU . TST DUP2 SHOULD DUP2 END

CLR . 1 2 DRP . 1 EQU . TST DRP SHOULD DROP END

// 2.3: Logic Functions

CLR . 0 T? . 0 EQU . TST 0 T? SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 1 T? . 1 EQU . TST 1 T? SHOULD BE 1 END

CLR . 1 F? . 0 EQU . TST 1 F? SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 0 F? . 1 EQU . TST 0 F? SHOULD BE 1 END

CLR . 1 1 NEQ . 0 EQU . TST 1 1 NEQ SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 1 2 NEQ . 1 EQU . TST 1 2 NEQ SHOULD BE 1 END

CLR . 0 0 AND . 0 EQU . TST 0 0 AND SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 0 1 AND . 0 EQU . TST 0 1 AND SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 1 0 AND . 0 EQU . TST 1 0 AND SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 1 1 AND . 1 EQU . TST 1 1 AND SHOULD BE 1 END

CLR . 0 0 OR . 0 EQU . TST 0 0 OR SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 0 1 OR . 1 EQU . TST 0 1 OR SHOULD BE 1 END
CLR . 1 0 OR . 1 EQU . TST 1 0 OR SHOULD BE 1 END
CLR . 1 1 OR . 1 EQU . TST 1 1 OR SHOULD BE 1 END

CLR . 0 0 XOR . 0 EQU . TST 0 0 XOR SHOULD BE 0 END
CLR . 0 1 XOR . 1 EQU . TST 0 1 XOR SHOULD BE 1 END
CLR . 1 0 XOR . 1 EQU . TST 1 0 XOR SHOULD BE 1 END
CLR . 1 1 XOR . 0 EQU . TST 1 1 XOR SHOULD BE 0 END
